# Tool E2E Fixtures

This directory contains E2E test fixtures for all 122+ tool domains.

## Structure

Each domain has its own fixture file:
- `habits.fixture.json`
- `career.fixture.json`
- `memory.fixture.json`
- etc.

## Generation

Run `ferni tools generate-fixtures` to auto-generate fixture stubs for all tools.
Use `--force` to overwrite existing fixtures.

## Format

```json
{
  "domain": "habits",
  "description": "E2E fixtures for habits domain tools",
  "generatedAt": "2026-01-19T...",
  "tools": [
    {
      "id": "tool-trackHabit",
      "category": "tool",
      "toolId": "trackHabit",
      "toolDomain": "habits",
      "name": "Track Habit",
      "description": "Track daily habit completion",
      "tags": ["habits"],
      "testParams": {
        "userId": "{testUserId}",
        "habitId": "test-habit-id"
      },
      "expectedStorage": [
        {
          "path": "bogle_users/{userId}/habits",
          "exists": true,
          "requiredFields": ["name", "frequency"]
        }
      ],
      "expectedInsight": {
        "anyInsight": true
      },
      "incomplete": true
    }
  ]
}
```

## Fixture States

- `incomplete: true` - Auto-generated stub, needs manual verification
- `skip: true` - Skip this test, with `skipReason`
- No flags - Ready for E2E validation
